graph TB
    Query([User Query]) --> Classify{Query Complexity?}
    
    Classify -->|Simple factual| ZS[Zero-Shot<br/>$0.001 / 85-92%]
    Classify -->|Needs specific format| FS[Few-Shot<br/>$0.005 / +5-15%]
    Classify -->|Math / logic / policy| CoT[Chain-of-Thought<br/>$0.002 / +10-25%]
    Classify -->|High-stakes decision| SC[Self-Consistency<br/>$0.005 x5 / ~95%]
    Classify -->|Architecture / strategy| ToT[Tree-of-Thought<br/>$0.003 x3 / best path]
    
    ZS --> Accuracy{Accuracy > 90%?}
    Accuracy -->|Yes| Ship[Ship It]
    Accuracy -->|No| FS
    
    FS --> FmtOK{Format correct?}
    FmtOK -->|Yes| Ship
    FmtOK -->|No| Structured
    
    subgraph Structured [Structured Output]
        XML[XML Tags<br/>Any model] 
        JSON[JSON Mode<br/>API feature]
        Instructor[instructor + Pydantic<br/>INDUSTRY STANDARD]
        Outlines[Outlines<br/>Local models only]
    end
    
    CoT --> Verify{Need certainty?}
    Verify -->|No| Ship
    Verify -->|Yes| SC
    
    SC --> Ship
    ToT --> Ship
    
    Ship --> SystemPrompt
    
    subgraph SystemPrompt [System Prompt — 4 Pillars]
        Persona[Persona: who you are]
        Constraints[Constraints: what you never do]
        Format[Format: how you respond]
        Guardrails[Guardrails: edge cases]
    end
    
    SystemPrompt --> InjectionDefense
    
    subgraph InjectionDefense [Injection Defense — 4 Layers]
        direction TB
        ID1[Layer 1: Delimiters ~70%<br/>User input in tagged box]
        ID2[Layer 2: Sanitize ~90%<br/>Strip attack patterns]
        ID3[Layer 3: Hierarchy ~98%<br/>Unbreakable system rules]
        ID4[Layer 4: Output Scan ~99.9%<br/>Check response for leaks]
        ID1 --> ID2 --> ID3 --> ID4
    end
    
    InjectionDefense --> Response([Safe Response])
    
    subgraph Versioning [Prompt Lifecycle]
        Git[Git + PR Review] --> Test[Golden Dataset Test]
        Test --> Canary[Canary 10%]
        Canary --> Deploy[Full Deploy]
    end

    style ZS fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
    style FS fill:#1f6feb,color:#fff
    style CoT fill:#8957e5,color:#fff
    style SC fill:#d29922,color:#fff
    style ToT fill:#da3633,color:#fff
    style Instructor fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
    style Ship fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
    style ID4 fill:#3fb950,color:#fff
